Malt drinks contain Vitamin B6, fibre, potassium and folate that lower cholesterol and decrease the risk of cardiac diseases. Milk is a source of Vitamins A and D, protein, potassium, and calcium, aids in sleeping and is highly nutritious to the body.
INGREDIENT
Malt
Milk
METHOD
Pour a bottle of malt into a glass cup, add a tin of milk and stir to combine.
Pour mix into a popsicle mould and cover. Place in a refrigerator and refrigerate for 3 hours.
Enjoy.
PS. If you were hoping to know if malt and milk will increase your blood, the answer is no